{"word":"Luke","slug":"luke","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Luke</b> A disciple.<br/> A physician<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=14'>Col 4:14</a><br/> Wrote to Theophilus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=4'>Luk 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=2'>Act 1:2</a><br/> Accompanies Paul:<br/> - In his tour of Asia and Macedonia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=13'>Act 16:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=6'>Act 20:6</a> <br/> - To Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=18'>Act 21:18</a> <br/> - To Rome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27'>Act 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=11'>2Ti 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=57&chapter=1&verse=24'>Phm 1:24</a> "}]}